A portal glows softly before you. You wonder where it leads.

Welcome to Rough Riders....

If you have become a member, it was because we felt you are a great player, and though there is no honor before humility, we believe Rough Riders need to prove their ability to join our guild.

So we present very difficult challenges as a requirement to join, also we are looking for people who don't complain a lot, and so if you were chosen to be a part of our guild, please keep that in mind.

Rough Riders love a great challenge, we like it rough, and we aren't afraid of the meanest and the baddest monsters, we don't complain, we just learn to adapt and overcome!  If ever you need help, just ask a guild member, we will be more than glad to help you where we can.

Enjoy your stay....
